title: Letting The Past Be The Past | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Letting The Past Be The Past | Joel Osteen
description:
If we want to experience the new things God has prepared for us, we have to learn to let go of the past. When you move on from the mistakes and disappointments, you're making room for God to release new blessings into your life. 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
